(Training Needs Survey)
to help boost her performance a little.

43
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,120
But in the end, her pitch convinced me.

44
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:05,160
I was tempted,

45
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:06,270
so I signed up.

46
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:09,100
The tuition fee is 6,000?

47
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:11,200
I don't have that much money.

48
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:16,040
(Loan Agreement)
We collaborate with a loan company.

49
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:17,320
If you take out a loan,

50
