51
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,280
20% discount?

52
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,240
Can there really be such a good deal?

53
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,600
I might as well be honest with you.

54
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,360
There're university graduates everywhere now.

55
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,060
For those of us running self-study training,

56
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:32,000
the pressure is immense.

57
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,240
To attract students,

58
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:35,000
we've had to keep cutting our profits.

59
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:36,800
Eventually,

60
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,160
her persuasive words won me over.

61
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:41,200
I ended up signing the contract.

62
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,680
Didn't you just sell a house to Bai Wu?

63
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,360
My brother's getting married.

64
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,720
Our family can't afford a wedding house.

65
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:53,120
My mom's been crying to me about it,

66
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,640
so I gave her the money.

67
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:56,560
You...!

68
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:59,080
Then... what happened next?

69
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,880
Hello? Hi, hello.

70
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:06,520
Is this Need Money Customer Service?

71
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,960
I'd like to ask something.

72
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,760
I borrowed 4,800 yuan.

73
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:12,080
Why did I only get 2,880?

74
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,320
We offer loans

75
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:17,360
with a handling fee and consultation fee.

76
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:20,440
Usually about 40% of the loan amount.

77
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,520
That's so high!

78
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,280
Then I don't want the loan.

79
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:25,920
Your loan has already been issued.

80
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:28,240
But you didn't send the money to me!

81
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,960
It was sent to the training institution.

82
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:32,200
You signed the loan contract yourself, right?

83
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:35,110
Yes, but...

84
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:37,760
We only recognize the signer of the contract.

85
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:57,240
Later, I realized they were working together.

86
00:03:57,680 --> 00:04:01,000
I thought I was just scammed out of 4,800.

87
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:04,000
My monthly base salary is 2,000 yuan.

88
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,200
If I save carefully, I can pay it back.

89
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:08,280
But last month, my brother got married.

90
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:11,200
My mom bragged about me in front of others.

91
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:14,320
She said I found a good job in the city.

92
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,920
Then she asked me for a wedding gift.

93
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:20,160
I ended up giving 2,000 yuan as a gift.

94
00:04:20,900 --> 00:04:22,160
They're like leeches.

95
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,720
I originally thought 800 yuan a month,

96
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:28,200
with 3% interest, was manageable.

97
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,640
But I never expected...

98
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,080
Well,

99
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,110
how could you do this?

100
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:35,880
I was just ten days late on the payment.

101
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,640
My monthly installment was 800 yuan.

102
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,040
Interest rate is 3%.

103
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:41,720
How did 4,800 turn into 8,500?

104
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:44,880
The 3% interest is calculated daily

105
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,680
and compounded based on the 4,800.

106
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:49,520
Overdue payments incur additional fees.

107
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,680
No, no.

108
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,320
This is way too unfair!

109
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,720
How am I supposed to pay this off?

110
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,880
Hold on, don't panic.

111
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:59,040
We're just following standard procedures.

112
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:01,280
