118
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,400
From that time,

119
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,160
I borrowed from one app

120
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,280
to pay off another loan.

121
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:23,000
Robbing Peter to pay Paul.

122
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:26,040
Even if I only eat two buns every day,

123
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,360
I still can't make ends meet.

124
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,240
The interest keeps compounding,

125
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,880
and the debt just grows bigger.

126
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,080
I'm honestly terrified.

127
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:39,240
I've deleted all loan apps,

128
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:42,360
and blocked unknown callers.

129
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:46,360
I thought I could escape it.

130
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,480
Stay away from her.

131
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:48,880
Don't let her drag you down.

132
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,920
If she asks for money, say no.

133
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,280
It's a bottomless pit.

134
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,600
She borrows but never repays.

135
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,600
Look at the mess you've caused.

136
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:03,220
(Pay the money, or your family will die)

137
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,400
