143
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,120
I didn't.

144
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,760
Can you give me a little more time?

145
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:23,400
It's not that I don't want to pay.

146
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:24,560
